reviewText: Love these just trying to complete my library
Got all seasons up to the current and love them all. High quality video, good attitudes and not too much product plugging.

Really what can I say about these videos.... If you are looking at them then you must be a bone collector fan. I have watched them twice and still enjoy the fun and excitement of watching these guys hunt.
My husband really wanted this for Christmas.  Could not find it in the stores.  Glad I found it online.  He is very happy.
Hunters of white tail deer everywhere, you will like this if you are anything like the gun toting, arrow siting, deer stand climbing, no scent washing crowd we have around our house.
The DVD set was in perfect new condition and it was a great season and looking forward to the next one.
Best hunting show there is.  Great hunts.  Waddell and the boys are hilarious.  Love how it follows them at camp as well as during the hunt.
